# Regression (issue #399): a Level-5 "street" repositions between drawings with
# already-taught RELATIVE movement only — never set_xy/set_heading, which name a
# coordinate/absolute heading and are a Level-6 concept. pen_up lifts the pen so the
# turn-and-forward reposition moves the turtle WITHOUT drawing; pen_down resumes drawing.
forward 10
pen_up
right 90
forward 10
pen_down
forward 10
